<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>ạ̉nạ yạ yswʿ lmạ ạfkr</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạ̉nạ yạ yswʿ lmạ ạ̉fkr .. ḥbytny qd ạ̹yh?
 qd ạ̹yh? .. qd ạ̹yh?
 hạfḍl ṭwl ʿmry ạ̉sẖkr .. wḥbk ạ̉frḥ byh
 ạ̉frḥ byh .. ạ̉frḥ byh
 ḥbtny mn zmạn .. wạnạ mạstạhlsẖ ḥnạn
 wnzlt mn ạlsmạ .. fy ṣwrẗ ạ̹nsạn
 wʿsẖạn ḥbk ʿjyb .. rḍyt mwt ạlṣlyb
 wṣrt lyk qryb .. wạbn kmạn</lyrics>
<hymn_number>867</hymn_number>
<author>mnạl smyr, mnạl smyr</author>
</song>